[[File:Hiroshige-100-views-of-edo-fox-fires.jpg|thumb|"Kitsunebi on New Year's Night under the Enoki Tree near Ōji" in the ''[[One Hundred Famous Views of Edo]]'' by Hiroshige. Each fox has a kitsunebi floating close to their face.]]
